    <div style="margin:40px">
        <center><h2>How to use</h2></center><br /><br />

        <h4>Step 1:</h4><br />
        <p>Click on any <b>Category</b></p><br />
        <img style="width:60%; margin-left:20%" src="~/uploads/a.png" />

        <h4>Step 2:</h4><br />
        <p>Select your desired products</p><br />
        <img style="width:60%; margin-left:20%" src="~/uploads/b.png" /><br /><br />

        <h4>Step 3:</h4><br />
        <p>Click on <b>View Cart</b> button scroll cart item here you can edit quantity and remove product from cart </p><br /><br />
