        <h4>Step 5:</h4><br />
        <p>Note your 8 digit tracking number and here your order, given details and admin will send 8 digit tracking number on your mobile Number  </p><br /><br />
        <img style="width:60%; margin-left:20%" src="~/uploads/f.png" /><br /><br />

        <h3>In the rest of time if you want to track your order status  </h3><br />

        <h4>Step 1:</h4><br />
        <p>Click on right side of navigation on <b>TRACK YOUR ORDER</b> button</p><br /><br />
        <img style="width:60%; margin-left:20%" src="~/uploads/g.png" /><br /><br />

        <h4>Step 2:</h4><br />
        <p>Insert your tacking number click on <b>GET STATUS</b> for order status </p><br /><br />
        <img style="width:60%; margin-left:20%" src="~/uploads/h.png" /><br /><br />
